  "sketchCode": "// Example: Servo Sweep\n// Sweep a servo back and forth from 0 to 180 degrees.\n\n#include <Servo.h>\n\nServo myServo;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  myServo.attach(9);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  for (int pos = 0; pos <= 180; pos++) {\n    myServo.write(pos);\n    delay(15);\n  }\n  for (int pos = 180; pos >= 0; pos--) {\n    myServo.write(pos);\n    delay(15);\n  }\n}\n",
